Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ We\N♪ Are the crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Gems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ We'll always save the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Steven: ♪ And if you think\Nwe can't, we'll ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Always find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ That's why the people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Garnet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Amethyst: ♪ Amethyst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pearl: ♪ And pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就进入表演\NAnd then we go into the tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我真心觉得【遛狗】那招\NBut I really think we should save the dogwalker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,应该留到下次\Nfor next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的第一印象 得搞得浮夸点\NThis is our first impression. We gotta go big.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们也应该赶紧行动 免得她们怀疑\NAnd we should go soon, too, before they get suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这俩人表现的非常可疑哇\NThose two are acting very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要问问他们在干啥吗\NShould we ask them what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 紫晶\NSteven, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是不是有啥事准备告诉我们呀\NIs there something you'd like to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛你们应该知道我们最近在副宝宝基地有一场\NSo you guys know how we recently had an epic showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,史诗级别的决战\Nin the beta kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也知道 在那时候 我们打败了铁石英\NAnd you know that during it, we beat Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们知道\NBut do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谁打败了她吗\Nwho beat Jasper?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩吗\NYou two?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,橄榄石\NPeridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她们没猜到\NIt didn't land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,直接切入正题 切入正题\NPick it back up. Pick it back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,咳咳 我们这有个人希望与你们见见面\NAhem! We have someone we'd like you to meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 就让我们见见这位神秘的陌生人吧\NAll right, let's meet this mysterious stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿呀 我是烟晶\NHeya. I'm Smoky Quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你们真是愉快\NNice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-啥-噢\N-What?!-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别急着提起吓掉的袜子\NDon't bother putting your socks back on,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,精彩的还在后头呢\N'cause I'm about to knock 'em off again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你们应该能看出我是怎么打败铁石英的了\NNow, you guys can see exactly how I beat Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这一招我喜欢叫【与狗漫步】\NThis is a little trick I like to call "Walk the Dog"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 谁来解释下这一切\NWait! Explain everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这招叫【与狗慢跑】\NThis one's called "Jog the Dog"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 哈 这招叫\NWhoops! Ha! Uh, this one is called
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,【遛狗只是我白天的工作\N"Dog Walking's Just My Day Job
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,直到面试结果出来为止】\NTill I Finally Get That Callback"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,石榴 帮个忙\NGarnet, a little help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗯嗯嗯 -红纹玛瑙\NMnh-mnh-mnh!  Sardonyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道室内玩儿武器的规定的\NYou know the rules about weapons in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数情况可以使用 但是有一些例外\NMostly allowed, really,but with some exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真是荣幸\NOh, what a pleasure it is to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经留下了很深的“印象”了\NYou've made quite the impression already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 墙上那边有一个 还有那里……\NIn fact, there's one in the wall over there and there and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 抱歉 看来刚才我有点控计不住我记己\NUh, sorry. Looks like I got  bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我会 呃 收敛一点\NI can, uh...reel it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 别再这么做了\NBut really, please -- stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才的表演真是太棒了\NYour act is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是给你展示的舞台太小了\NBut your stage is too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要更大的空间来了解一下彼此\NWe need some space to get to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,比如一个…更无限的地方\NSomewhere a bit more... infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你在神庙里有一个专属房间?\NYou have a room in the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我存在 它就存在\NIt exists as long as  I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在…我...进去了\NAnd here...I...am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快来 别害羞\NCome now, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在嘛都看不见\NI can't see nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的你看不见任何东西 亲爱的 \NYou cannot see anything, my darling --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为演出还没开始呢\Nbecause the show hasn't started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,演出?\NShow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来自神庙深处的超自然房间的直播\NLive, from a metaphysical room deep in the temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到“今夜玛瑙秀”\Nit's "Sardonyx Tonight"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大家晚上好\NGood evening, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我们迎来了一个全新的融合体\NWe have a brand-new fusion with us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直要兴奋到要碎掉\NI'm so excited, I could just shatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,掌声欢迎--烟晶\NEveryone welcome Smoky Quartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么快告诉我\NSo tell me, literally,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所有关于你的事\Neverything there is to know about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跳过任何有料的细节哦\NAnd do not skip out on any of the juicy details.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 我挺喜欢在宝宝基地长距离漫步\NWell, I like, uh, long walks through the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 我就是在那里成型的\Nactually,that's where I stored up became me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 呃 嘭 --打败了铁石英\NAnd, uh, pow --beat Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 就是那个铁石英 不断在宝宝基地出没\NOh, that Jasper, always running 'round kindergartens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,四处捣乱\Nand causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,果然最后结局不好呢\NBoy, that didn't quite work out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜她得回学前班了 是吧 各位\NGuess she should go back to preschool, am I right, folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她在与一个堕转宝石的融合时完全发疯了\NShe lost her mind in a corrupted fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你可以说她进行了一次…短暂的融合\NI guess you could say she had a...short fuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,观众挺友好,是吧?\NEasy crowd, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里找来的?\NWhere'd you get 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我变出来的\NI made them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但烟晶 我想我们真正好奇的是…\NBut, Smoky, I think what we really want to know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟是谁\Nwho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,烟晶…是谁\NWho is...Smoky...Quartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 嘛 现在加上战斗的时候\NUh, well, between the fight and now, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我总共才存在了 大概 十分钟 所以 呃\NI've only really existed for, like, 10 minutes, so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我不知道\NI-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道怎么做这个 \NBut I do know how to do this! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这招叫【裹在纸尿裤里的忧郁婴儿】\NThis one's called "Sad Baby in a Diaper"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对 溜溜球\NYes, the yo-yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看过 体验过 喜欢过\NSeen it,lived it,loved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你有其他的技能吗\NBut what about the rest of your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的把戏哪有扑克牌那么多啦\NI ain't exactly a deck of cards here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我倒可以舔到我的胳膊肘\NI  can lick my elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我可有三个咧\NI have three of them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在由赞助商讲两句话,广告之后马上回来\NWe'll be right back after a word from our sponsor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 小烟 让我们来一场融合体之间的对话\N Listen, Smoky, let's talk -- fusion to fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你的溜溜球确实不错 但我更想了解你本人\NThat's a nice yo-yo, but I want to know the yo-you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小烟 你除了溜溜球之外肯定\NSmoky, there's bound to be way more to you than just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还有更多\Na yo-yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个融合体\NYou're a fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是充满了惊喜的\NYou're full of surprises!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只是你现在还不知道罢了\NYou just don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对,对啊,惊喜就是你不知道的事嘛\NYeah. Yeah, I guess that{\i1} is{\i} how surprises work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到了!\NI've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,每个融合都会获得一些新的东西\NEvery fusion gets something new --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,比如一种新能力,或者新武器\Na new power, a new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,比如悠悠球?\NLike a yo-yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对,但比那好\NYes, but better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来找找你身上有什么新的地方\NLet's find out what's new about{\i1} you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来!\NAnd welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那些卡通人物肯定让你\NDon't those cartoon characters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,超想买她们的周边对吧\Nmake you want to buy those products?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿如此,不然我就没钱赚了\NI sure hope so,or else I'd be off air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我们为你准备了一个新环节\NWe have a new segment for you all tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没错,各位\NThat's right, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在进入“打-个-鸟”\NIt's time to Hit That Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,欧珀在天空塔的冒险当中\NDuring Opal's adventures at the sky spire,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她用弓箭打掉了一群怪物鸟\Nshe took down a flock ofbird monsters with her bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来看看你有没有她的“珀”力吧\NLet's see if you've got her "opalescent" aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想,小烟?\NWhat do you say, Smoky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好打个鸟了吗?\NAre you ready to Hit That Bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,啊,这个,弓箭也算一种悠悠球是吧?\NOh! Ah, well, a bow is kind of like a yo-yo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,除了上面的弦方向不一样还有...\NExcept if the string went this a ways and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始,如何?\NLet's start, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,时间可不等人哦!\NTime is an impatient thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哦,时间到\NUh-oh, time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来看看\NLet's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,分数加起来是\NThe score tallies to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一,二,三...\None, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,零分\Nzero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我真是持盾呢,哈\NGuess I'm a real bow-zo, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们向前进入下一个环节如何啊,各位?\NWhat do you say we move on to the next segment, everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了!\NHere we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我把这个环节叫...\NI call this segment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗,小个子?\NYou Like That, Little Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为人人都喜欢往期回顾嘛\N'Cause everybody loves a callback.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有真的出演本集\NShe's not actually in this episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样还要付她工资吗\NDo we still have to pay her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要?好吧\NYes? Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好,融合之后能力会提升,这已是公开的秘密了\NNow, it's no secret that us fine fusions pack an extra punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,苏纪石因其强有力\NBut Sugilite is a standout
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,的击打能力而鹤立鸡群\Nfor being a heavy hitting powerhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也许你有一些比苏纪石更厉害的招数?\NBut maybe you've got something to top Sugilite's swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,也许吧?\NMmm, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个槌来击打垫子\NJust hit the base with this mallet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看你能力有多强\Nand we'll see how you measure up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这水平?\NThat all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,天了\NGosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!非常接近了!\NOoh! Very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,加上一些旋转动作会更好哦\NAn extra spin around always helps me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,旋转动作,是吗?\NAn extra spin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈,想得美!\N{\i1}Ha ha! Nice try!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啥!\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次!\NOne more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你...啥也...不是!\N{\i1}You...ain't...nothing!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,好\NHmm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,确实有什么不对的地方\NSomething just isn't hitting right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你的强壮\NMaybe you're just strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♪表现在别处 \N♪In a different way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快回来\NWe'll find out in just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放出场音乐,乔治\NPlay us over to stage right,Jorge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,别担心那些观众\NOkay, don't worry about that crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也别想乔治了,就只有你和我\NDon't worry about Jorge.It's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊,没问题\NYeah, no duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...谁是乔治啊?\NActually...who's Jorge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小烟,你不要隐藏实力\NSmoky,you're holding out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好看你的能力了\NI'm ready to see your main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊,我也是\NAh, you and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好,亚历山大石有喷火的能力\NNow, Alexandrite has a throat full of flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不造这是不是她嗓音沙哑的原因\NWhether that's the cause of her raspy voice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个先放一边\Nis up for debate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是毫无疑问的是她攻击时--\Nbut there's no room for questions when she attacks --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,会吐出烈焰!\Nexhaling a burning blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我把这个环节叫“火之吐息”\NSo I call this segment"Breath of Fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,玛瑙,我不确定啊\NSardonyx, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧,小烟\NCome on, Smoky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,站上舞台试试看\NStep up and see if you can spit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能吐出一些火之元素\Nsome elemental chaos at the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们似乎遇到了一些魔法故障\NWe seem to experiencing some magical difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是别换台哦\NBut don't change the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文和紫晶一定有些共同点\NThere must be some common thread between Steven and Amethyst
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,成倍体现在他们的融合上\Nthat's heightened by their fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定啊,玛,我想,零加零不还是零吗\NI don't know, Sards, I guess,uh, zero plus zero equals zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想到一块去的事,他们做到一块去的事\NSomething they both think.Something they both do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,人说负负不得正嘛--\NThey say two wrongs don't make a right --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不就是典型的例子吗?\NI guess I'm living proof that{\i1} that's{\i} true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是一个大个儿的失败的...\NI'm just one big super wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,除了悠悠什么都不会的家伙\N...good-for-nothing dud with a yo-yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想给我们留下好印象!\NThey want to impress us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经准备了一个早上了\NThey were planning this all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抢了他们的风头!\NWe hijacked their show!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我过于兴奋了!\NI was excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我们俩的事!\NIt's not about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,发生啥事?!\NWhat's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是红纹玛瑙!\NIt's Sardonyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她不在这里,这个房间就不能存在!\NIf she's not here,the room can't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,石榴!\NGarnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,珍珠!\NPearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哈? \NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉降落有些颠簸\NSorry for the rough landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在说什么呢?!-简直太精彩了!\N-What are you talking about?!-That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,紫晶\NOh, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是为他树立了一个好榜样!\NYou've been such a good influence on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他是我的榜样了\NIt's kind of the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可告诉我们悠悠能当钩爪使\NYou didn't tell us that yo-yo can grapple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,悠悠能做很多事情呢\NIt can do so much stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等下,你是把它当绳圈还是鞭子用?\NWait. So do you use it like a lasso or a flail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-比鞭子好多了!-它是个玩具!\N-It's better than a flail.-It's a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是想不到\NIt's so unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把当时情况实况转播一下\NGive us the play-by-play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们当时在那...\NSo, there we were...
